<item>
            <title>[LU-15366] tbf: Increase maximum rpc rate for default rule</title>
                <link>https://jira.whamcloud.com/browse/LU-15366</link>
                <project id="10000" key="LU">Lustre</project>
                    <description>&lt;p&gt;The maximum rate for a tbf rule is 65535. &lt;br/&gt;
This rate could be problematic for the default rule for clusters with many clients.&lt;/p&gt;

&lt;p&gt;Rate is stored on an u32 or an __u64 and not on an u16, so the value can be increase easily.  &lt;/p&gt;</description>
